snippet.title: Tekken - iOS/Android - What's your next move? (Announcement Trailer)
snippet.description:
Tekken is coming to iOS and Android! Pre-register now to unlock free bonuses http://www.tekken-mobile.com. A soft launch available in Canada for now. We’ll announce more countries leading to the global launch later!

Like us: https://www.facebook.com/tekkeneu
Follow us: https://twitter.com/tekken
Visit us: https://www.tekken-mobile.com

Credits:
- Video editing: Old Skull Games http://www.oldskullgames.com
- Music & sound design: Gigawatts Productions http://www.gigawattsproductions.com/
